":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c801%2c20220323%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗交簡,801,20220323,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗交簡","JNO":"801","JDATE":"20220323","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}